{"tid":2075840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銅芯抗疫口罩多次滑落　林鄭月娥稱或洗得多「鬆咗」","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T07:03:18.000Z","uid":54800,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f101097857a45d568b6f995e19a9e8da8b67ded2","tid":2075840,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今日出席行政會議前見記者，她在開場發言時，佩戴的銅芯抗疫口罩多次滑落至鼻翼以下，林鄭月娥至少3次用手將口罩拉回至覆蓋鼻孔，但數分鐘後口罩再次滑落。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥主動提到，今日不知為何口罩「麻麻地」，可能是洗得多<strong>「鬆咗」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。在答問環節，她一度脫下整個口罩飲水。之後她的口罩再滑落，但她未有再整理，直至記者會完結。"},{"pid":"f8ed43f885dfcf6789f190ba1a8af1908983b368","tid":2075840,"uid":309553,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"性暗示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8efebeba3582962606054727bb7cee11465a2e","tid":2075840,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"識得除口罩飲水，依樣叻過老懵董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3878e8971310ce7e5d2218dfdf3fa772f741dd","tid":2075840,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:11:31.000Z","msg":"林鄭鬆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd7db1849577db893050b6b97883f880ce68d93","tid":2075840,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"屌, 阿婆你鬆咗關我哋香港市民鳩事咩<br />\n<br />\n你同你老公講啦"},{"pid":"ce5a0b2f1af0a1d15b160237a53e89d08e354bef","tid":2075840,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"周圍扑嘢"},{"pid":"49524a17b27cf5e9208d4d2d127b8d63a0aa86ed","tid":2075840,"uid":15861